184
00:20:12,230 --> 00:20:15,880
[Poseidon Department Store]

185
00:20:30,950 --> 00:20:32,740
Hai Yi?

186
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:38,079
Chairman, we'll do our daily routine in the afternoon.

187
00:20:38,079 --> 00:20:40,650
Some other people will join us.

188
00:20:42,150 --> 00:20:44,280
That really is Hai Yi.

189
00:20:51,280 --> 00:20:55,260
Board members, thank you for being here despite your busy schedules.

190
00:20:55,260 --> 00:21:00,100
My older brother has just passed away. It's been hard for us.

191
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:03,220
However, we need someone to lead Poseidon Department Store.

192
00:21:03,220 --> 00:21:06,239
Today, I'm going to make an announcement.

193
00:21:06,239 --> 00:21:08,290
His son will inherit the business.

194
00:21:08,290 --> 00:21:10,729
Hai Yi will be the next chairman,

195
00:21:10,729 --> 00:21:13,119
