204
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:40,589
Vice Chairman Wu, do you have a better candidate in mind?

205
00:21:40,589 --> 00:21:43,800
Of course I do. Managing Director Liang is very experienced.

206
00:21:43,800 --> 00:21:47,510
He helped Chairman run the company for years. To me,

207
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:49,490
